<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>PSG College of Technology - Final Semester Internship</title>
  <style>
    @page {
      size: A4;
      margin: 15mm 18mm 12mm 18mm;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      font-size: 10pt;
      color: #000;
      line-height: 1.4;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .page {
      width: 100%;
      page-break-after: always;
    }
    .page:last-child {
      page-break-after: avoid;
    }

    /* ── College header ── */
    .college-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .college-name {
      font-size: 12pt;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .form-title {
      font-size: 10.5pt;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    /* ── Paragraphs ── */
    p {
      margin: 3px 0;
      font-size: 10pt;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    /* ── Tables ── */
    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin: 4px 0;
      font-size: 9.5pt;
    }
    td, th {
      border: 1px solid #000;
      padding: 3px 5px;
      vertical-align: top;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }
    th {
      font-weight: bold;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 9pt;
    }
    .no-border td {
      border: none;
      padding: 1px 2px;
    }

    /* ── Lists ── */
    ol {
      margin: 3px 0 3px 18px;
      padding: 0;
    }
    ol li {
      font-size: 10pt;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
    ol.alpha {
      list-style-type: lower-alpha;
      margin-left: 22px;
    }
    ol.alpha li {
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    /* ── Utility ── */
    .small     { font-size: 9pt; }
    .italic    { font-style: italic; }
    .bold      { font-weight: bold; }
    .center    { text-align: center; }
    .right     { text-align: right; }
    .underline { text-decoration: underline; }

    /* ── Sig lines ── */
    .sig-line {
      display: inline-block;
      border-top: 1px solid #000;
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 2px;
      font-size: 9.5pt;
    }

    .page-footer { text-align: center; font-size: 9pt; margin-top: 6px; }
    .pto { text-align: right; font-size: 9pt; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 2px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ═══════════════ PAGE 1 ═══════════════ -->
<div class="page">

  <div class="college-header">
    <div class="college-name">PSG COLLEGE OF TECHNOLOGY, COIMBATORE 641 004</div>
    <div class="form-title">Undertaking for Pursuing Internship in the Final Semester (UG/PG)</div>
  </div>

  <!-- Date on right, From on left — same line -->
  <table class="no-border" style="margin:3px 0 2px 0;">
    <tr>
      <td style="width:60%;"></td>
      <td style="width:40%; text-align:right; font-size:10pt;"><strong>Date:</strong> {{currentDate}}</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <p>From</p>
  <p>{{student_name}}</p>
  <p>{{roll_number}}</p>

  <p style="margin-top:5px;">To</p>
  <p>The Principal</p>
  <p>PSG College of Technology</p>
  <p>Coimbatore &#8211; 641004</p>

  <p style="margin-top:3px;">Through : THE HEAD OF THE DEPARTMENT, DEPARTMENT OF {{#if department}}{{department}}{{else}}--------------------------{{/if}}</p>

  <p style="margin-top:3px;">Dear Sir,</p>

  <p style="margin-top:2px;"><strong>Sub:</strong> Undertaking while pursuing Internship/Project Work II in Industry / Institutions.</p>

  <p style="margin-top:3px;">I wish to inform that, I have been offered internship in the organization, details of which are provided below. The activities carried out during this internship will be adequate for completing Project Work II(Code&#x2026;&#x2026;&#x2026;&#x2026;&#x2026;&#x2026;..) as per the recommendations of the Guide and the project review committee.</p>

  <!-- Internship details table — exact column layout from official PDF -->
  <table style="margin-top:4px;">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th rowspan="2" style="width:26%; text-align:center;">Name &amp; Address of the<br>Industry / Institution</th>
        <th colspan="2" style="text-align:center;">Internship Period</th>
        <th rowspan="2" style="width:22%; text-align:center;">Guide from the<br>industry / institution<br>with contact details</th>
        <th rowspan="2" style="width:11%; text-align:center;">Guide in the<br>department</th>
        <th rowspan="2" style="width:13%; text-align:center;">Stipend<br>receivable (if any)</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th style="width:9%;">From (Date)</th>
        <th style="width:9%;">To (Date)</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td style="height:45px; vertical-align:top;">
          {{#if company_name}}{{company_name}}<br>{{/if}}
          {{#if company_address}}{{company_address}}<br>{{/if}}
          {{#if company_city}}{{company_city}}{{#if company_state}}, {{company_state}}{{/if}}{{/if}}
        </td>
        <td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;">{{start_date}}</td>
        <td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;">{{end_date}}</td>
        <td style="vertical-align:top;">
          {{#if guide_name_industry}}{{guide_name_industry}}<br>{{/if}}
          {{#if guide_contact}}{{guide_contact}}{{/if}}
        </td>
        <td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;">{{#if guide_name_dept}}{{guide_name_dept}}{{/if}}</td>
        <td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;">{{#if stipend_amount}}&#8377; {{stipend_amount}}{{else}}NIL{{/if}}</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <p style="margin-top:4px;">I request you to permit me to accept the offer of internship and provide attendance for the duration mentioned.</p>
  <p style="margin-top:3px;"><strong>I hereby undertake the following.</strong></p>

  <ol style="margin-top:3px;">
    <li>I will be regular and sincere in carrying out my internship at the above organization and I will obey the Rules and Regulations of the organization.</li>
    <li>My attendance will be sent regularly to my department by the Industry / Institution.</li>
    <li>I will attend all the project work II reviews scheduled in the department and submit the report for my Project Work II on or before the deadline specified by the Department.</li>
    <li>I will update the guide in the college regularly through reports reviewed by the guide in the industry.</li>
    <li>*I have completed all course work except Project Work II to become eligible for the award of the Degree.</li>
    <li>*I have 1 / 2 final semester elective course/s for which I have registered along with other students. I will study the course/s under self study mode and I will appear for all CA Evaluation Tests/Tutorials in the above course/s.</li>
    <li>I have enclosed the offer letter for internship.</li>
    <li>I am aware of internship and conversion to full time offer and I will abide by the rules of Placement &amp; Training Office.</li>
    <li>I have enclosed my parent's permission letter to carry out the internship/Project work.</li>
    <li><sup>#</sup>I am not in receipt of any other scholarship/Stipend from the company (Applicable to PG AICTE GATE Scholarship/ PG NON GATE State Government Scholarship Students)</li>
    <li>*If I intend to receive stipend from the company, I am aware that, I will not be eligible to receive the PG Scholarship receiving from AICTE /State Government during the period of my paid internship.</li>
  </ol>

  <p class="small" style="margin-top:4px;">*Strike out if not applicable.<br>
  <sup>#</sup> PG GATE Student has to produce a letter from the company in their letter head to this effect.</p>

  <p class="small italic" style="margin-top:3px;">Note: Do not edit the format</p>

  <!-- Page 1 sig row — signature of student on right, others on left -->
  <table class="no-border" style="margin-top:14px;">
    <tr>
      <td style="width:36%; font-size:9.5pt; vertical-align:bottom;">Tutor/Programme Co-ordinator</td>
      <td style="width:20%; text-align:center; font-size:9.5pt; vertical-align:bottom;">Guide</td>
      <td style="width:14%; text-align:center; font-size:9.5pt; vertical-align:bottom;">HoD</td>
      <td style="width:30%; text-align:right; font-size:9.5pt; vertical-align:bottom;">(Signature of the Student)</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <div class="page-footer">Page 1/2</div>
  <div class="pto">(PTO)</div>

</div><!-- end page 1 -->


<!-- ═══════════════ PAGE 2 ═══════════════ -->
<div class="page">

  <!-- Page 2 starts directly with Recommendation — no college header -->
  <p class="center underline bold" style="font-size:11pt; margin:0 0 8px 0;">Recommendation from the department</p>

  <p style="margin-bottom:4px;"><strong>Academic details of the student:</strong></p>

  <!-- NAME / Roll Number / CGPA all on one line -->
  <table class="no-border" style="margin:2px 0 5px 0;">
    <tr>
      <td style="width:9%; font-size:10pt;"><strong>NAME:</strong></td>
      <td style="width:32%; font-size:10pt;">{{student_name}}</td>
      <td style="width:18%; font-size:10pt;"><strong>Roll Number:</strong></td>
      <td style="width:22%; font-size:10pt;">{{roll_number}}</td>
      <td style="width:8%; font-size:10pt;"><strong>CGPA:</strong></td>
      <td style="width:11%; font-size:10pt;">{{#if cgpa_value}}{{cgpa_value}}{{/if}}</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <!-- Academic status table — 4 columns, many blank rows -->
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th style="width:25%;">Number of Pending Redo<br>courses with Course Code<br>&amp; Title</th>
        <th style="width:25%;">Number of Pending RA<br>courses with Course Code &amp;<br>Title</th>
        <th style="width:30%;">Pending Courses of<br>current semester with<br>Course Code &amp; Title</th>
        <th style="width:20%;">REMARKS</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr style="height:20px;">
        <td>{{#if redo_courses}}{{redo_courses}}{{/if}}</td>
        <td>{{#if ra_courses}}{{ra_courses}}{{/if}}</td>
        <td>{{#if pending_courses}}{{pending_courses}}{{/if}}</td>
        <td></td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="height:20px;"><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr>
      <tr style="height:20px;"><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr>
      <tr style="height:20px;"><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr>
      <tr style="height:20px;"><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr>
      <tr style="height:20px;"><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr>
      <tr style="height:20px;"><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr>
      <tr style="height:20px;"><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <p style="margin-top:5px;">The work assigned by the industry /institution <strong>meets</strong> the academic standards for Project Work II.<br>
  This student has not accepted any other internship.</p>

  <p style="margin-top:4px; font-size:9.5pt;">*This student has accepted another internship but has declined the same due to academic/ health/ financial reasons. The company/institution is informed of his inability to accept the offer through letter/email. The details of the organization is given below.</p>

  <!-- Declined internship table -->
  <table style="margin-top:4px;">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th rowspan="2" style="width:28%;">Name &amp; Address of the<br>Industry / Institution</th>
        <th colspan="2">Internship Period</th>
        <th rowspan="2" style="width:25%;">Guide from the<br>industry / institution<br>with contact details</th>
        <th rowspan="2" style="width:13%;">Guide in the<br>department</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th style="width:11%;">From (Date)</th>
        <th style="width:11%;">To (Date)</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr style="height:38px;">
        <td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <p style="margin-top:5px;">This student can be permitted to accept the internship and complete Project Work II within the specified time period.</p>

  <!-- Sig row 1 — spaced out naturally -->
  <table class="no-border" style="margin-top:35px;">
    <tr>
      <td style="width:26%; border-top:1px solid #000; text-align:center; font-size:9.5pt; padding-top:2px;">Tutor/Programme Coordinator</td>
      <td style="width:4%;"></td>
      <td style="width:16%; border-top:1px solid #000; text-align:center; font-size:9.5pt; padding-top:2px;">Guide</td>
      <td style="width:4%;"></td>
      <td style="width:14%; border-top:1px solid #000; text-align:center; font-size:9.5pt; padding-top:2px;">HoD</td>
      <td style="width:4%;"></td>
      <td style="width:32%; border-top:1px solid #000; text-align:center; font-size:9.5pt; padding-top:2px;">Dean, Placement &amp; Training</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <!-- Sig row 2 -->
  <table class="no-border" style="margin-top:30px;">
    <tr>
      <td style="width:38%; border-top:1px solid #000; text-align:center; font-size:9.5pt; padding-top:2px;">Dean - Academic</td>
      <td style="width:14%;"></td>
      <td style="width:48%; border-top:1px solid #000; text-align:center; font-size:9.5pt; padding-top:2px;">Principal</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <p class="small" style="margin-top:6px;">*Strike out if not applicable.</p>

  <!-- NOTE — in normal flow, not fixed -->
  <div style="margin-top:10px; font-size:9.5pt; line-height:1.4;">
    <strong>NOTE:</strong>&nbsp; 1. Original Form shall be submitted to <strong>Placement Office</strong><br>
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2. Photo copies shall be submitted to<br>
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;a) Academic section<br>
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;b) Concerned Department
  </div>

  <div class="page-footer" style="margin-top:8px;">Page 2/2</div>

</div><!-- end page 2 -->

</body>
</html>